sentinel.led
Class ParameterList

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--sentinel.led.ParameterList
public class ParameterList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The ParameterList class denotes the list of parameters of a primitive event. It stores the parameters in a Hashtable. It also contains the TimeStamp of the event and the event instance.
